assert test_repo.get_top_n_commiters([]) is None
authors_list = [Commit(None, None, 'James', None, None)] * 3 + [Commit(None,
    None, 'John', None, None), Commit(None, None, 'JJ', None, None)]
assert test_repo.get_top_n_commiters(authors_list) == [('James', 3), (
    'John', 1), ('JJ', 1)]
authors_list = [Commit(None, None, 'James', None, None)] * 30 + [Commit(
    None, None, 'John', None, None)] * 10 + [Commit(None, None, 'JJ', None,
    None)] * 5
assert test_repo.get_top_n_commiters(authors_list, normailze_values=True) == [(
    'James', 5), ('John', 2), ('JJ', 1)]
